00:33:11,360 --> 00:33:12,000
at the gate later.

844
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:12,800
Alright.

845
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:13,760
Come, come.

846
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:15,002
Go, set off fireworks.

847
00:33:15,002 --> 00:33:16,111
Let's go to the fireworks!

848
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:17,360
Come, children.

849
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:20,000
At the beginning of the New Year, I'd like to say a few words.

850
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,000
This was a good year.

851
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:26,000
At the beginning of the year, I felt that there were six joys.

852
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,360
The first joy

853
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,840
is that all the children have come back from Shanghai

854
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:33,280
with Shizhi, Bai Lan, Xingang, and Liu Mei.

855
00:33:33,840 --> 00:33:35,600
For the first time in many years,

856
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:37,440
there are so many people in our family.

857
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:39,840
to celebrate the New Year together.

858
00:33:40,320 --> 00:33:41,120
Not easy.

859
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:42,480
The second joy

860
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:45,440
is Shizhi's wedding.

861
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:47,760
Thirteen years of long-distance running

862
00:33:47,920 --> 00:33:50,000
from the Qing Dynasty to the Republic of China,

863
00:33:50,320 --> 00:33:52,960
experienced two restorations, and finally reached a happy ending.

864
00:33:53,360 --> 00:33:54,560
What a legendary story.

865
00:33:55,040 --> 00:33:55,760
Yes, Shizhi.

866
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:57,440
But I heard that when Professor Huang Kan

867
00:33:57,760 --> 00:33:59,040
made your wedding

868
00:33:59,520 --> 00:34:01,280
into lesson plans in class,

869
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:02,960
it made the whole classroom laugh.

870
00:34:04,080 --> 00:34:06,320
That's Huang Kan making fun of Shizhi,

871
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:07,520
I didn't expect it to backfire.

872
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:09,440
Instead, it was publicity for Shizhi.

873
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,040
I really don't care.

874
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:13,040
If I can really become the target of the New Culture,

875
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:14,400
it will be my honor.

876
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:16,480
Uncle Chen, what about the third joy?

877
00:34:17,040 --> 00:34:18,960
The third joy is naturally you young people.

878
00:34:19,600 --> 00:34:21,600
The French study hall has finally been built.

879
00:34:22,160 --> 00:34:23,920
Although the nature of your studies was temporary,

880
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:25,040
I finally got you

881
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,640
from Shanghai to Beijing.

882
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:29,280
Beijing is the center of Greater China.

883
00:34:29,680 --> 00:34:32,240
It can improve your quality of life here.

884
00:34:32,720 --> 00:34:33,760
The fourth joy?

885
00:34:34,080 --> 00:34:35,840
The fourth joy is meatballs.

886
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:38,720
Big meatballs.

887
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:40,320
The circulation of our "New Youth"

888
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:42,000
has exceeded 10,000 copies

889
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:44,240
since peer editing was implemented,

890
00:34:44,640 --> 00:34:46,160
and it is still increasing rapidly.

891
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:47,440
What does this mean?

892
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:50,320
The wave of the New Culture is coming.

893
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:52,720
Shizhi, our efforts have not been in vain.

894
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,800
Great!

895
00:34:55,680 --> 00:34:56,560
The fifth joy!

896
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:59,440
The October Revolution took place in Russia last year.

897
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:01,040
The Bolshevik Party,

898
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,960
according to Marx's socialist theory,

899
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:04,800
led armed insurrections

900
00:35:05,040 --> 00:35:06,560
and established the world's first

901
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:08,160
socialist country.

902
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,880
I read their program and was very inspired.

903
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:13,040
It is likely to be our role model.

904
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:15,760
We should study the Russian path carefully.

905
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:18,000
Don't move all foreign things

906
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:19,760
to your home, okay?

907
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:21,760
Fine, the sixth joy

908
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,840
is our Red Building.

909
00:35:24,160 --> 00:35:25,360
It's about to open soon.

910
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:27,280
Mr. Cai has accepted the advice of Mr. Zhongfu

911
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:29,200
and Mr. Shouchang

912
00:35:29,520 --> 00:35:30,880
to build an open space

913
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:32,400
in our Red Building library

914
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:35,120
and hold a reading club with the cultural youth

915
00:35:35,520 --> 00:35:36,800
outside the school to learn together.

916
00:35:37,120 --> 00:35:38,000
Qiaonian, Yannian,

917
00:35:38,240 --> 00:35:39,200
Liu Mei, Bai Lan.

918
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:40,880
You can all come to this reading club.

919
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:42,160
We can also participate?

920
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:42,880
Of course!

921
00:35:43,120 --> 00:35:43,760
That's great!

922
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:44,960
Good!

923
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:45,440
Great!

924
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:46,480
The sixth joy!

925
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:48,240
Wasn't the sixth joy

926
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:49,840
said by everyone and Shizhi?

927
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:53,040
Well, it was the same thing anyways.

928
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,640
So be it.

929
00:35:55,120 --> 00:35:56,560
Everyone stick Spring Festival couplets. Let's eat!

930
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:57,440
Let's eat!

931
00:35:57,600 --> 00:35:57,920
Let's eat!

932
00:35:58,080 --> 00:35:59,040
Come, come, open the table.

933
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:00,640
Put it in the pigeon cage.

934
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,400
Zimei, Henian!

935
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:03,680
Go wash your hands with Mom.

936
00:36:04,800 --> 00:36:08,560
On New Year's Eve, snowflakes floated home,

937
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:12,640
and Li Dazhao, the noble man, came.

938
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:14,960
Li Dazhao!

939
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:18,480
The pork and cabbage dumplings

940
00:36:18,880 --> 00:36:21,760
are cheerful and festive!

941
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:24,320
Great!

942
00:36:24,640 --> 00:36:25,040
Great singing!

943
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:25,760
Great!

944
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:26,960
Shugui, you can sing!

945
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:29,280
You can sing even the Laoting drum in our hometown.

946
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:30,880
Just these two voices.

947
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,400
Let me help.

948
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:34,160
How about I give you all a piece?

949
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:36,160
Yeah!

950
00:36:36,240 --> 00:36:36,800
Do it!

951
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:37,520
Let's hear it!

952
00:36:37,680 --> 00:36:38,560
Just once! Just once!

953
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:48,400
Wrapped in silver, full of guests

954
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:52,720
on New Year's Eve.

955
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:55,920
Talking about family life.

956
00:36:56,720 --> 00:37:01,520
Asking the locals. Why is it so lively?

957
00:37:02,640 --> 00:37:10,480
The fellow villagers are all good neighbors.

958
00:37:10,720 --> 00:37:12,320
Great!

959
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:14,560
That was amazing!

960
00:37:15,040 --> 00:37:16,320
Great! Great!

961
00:37:17,040 --> 00:37:17,840
Dumplings are done!

962
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:19,040
Come and eat dumplings.

963
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,200
Have a dumpling first, sir.

964
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:21,920
Hot dumpling just out of the pot.

965
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:22,720
Give it to the children quickly.

966
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:23,040
Sir, have one first.

967
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:24,480
I know. Give it to the children first.

968
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:26,240
You sent so many things all the way.

969
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:27,280
If it weren't for you,

970
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:28,320
none of us would have lived this year.

971
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,120
Not at all.

972
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:30,000
Give it to the children first.

973
00:37:30,080 --> 00:37:31,760
Daughter-in-law, listen to Mr. Dazhao.

974
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,200
Let the children eat first.

975
00:37:33,920 --> 00:37:35,200
Children, eat dumplings!

976
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,480
Is it too hot?

977
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:40,320
Too hot?

978
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:41,920
Here, eat dumplings!

979
00:37:43,120 --> 00:37:43,760
Ma, you eat.

980
00:37:57,600 --> 00:38:00,000
Daughter-in-law, why are you crying for the New Year?

981
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:02,000
What's the matter, sister?

982
00:38:02,560 --> 00:38:04,720
The dumpling also let out the tears.

983
00:38:05,520 --> 00:38:07,200
I'm happy.

984
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:08,000
Ma, is it tasty?

985
00:38:08,240 --> 00:38:09,200
It's tasty, son!

986
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:10,560
Give the dumplings to everyone quickly.

987
00:38:11,680 --> 00:38:12,000
Put it down.

988
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:13,600
You don't know.

989
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:15,840
Before you came, you had a problem with me.

990
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:18,000
Say it, I've never

991
00:38:18,240 --> 00:38:19,520
had such a good day since my wedding.

992
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:20,480
On this New Year's Day,

993
00:38:21,040 --> 00:38:22,160
I've never eaten more than a few dumplings.

994
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,200
Look at our work sheds.

995
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,680
Which family has white flour?

996
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:29,120
Here! Here!

997
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:31,280
I'm telling you,

998
00:38:31,680 --> 00:38:32,880
the rich call it New Year

999
00:38:33,200 --> 00:38:34,560
The poor call it another day to survive.

1000
00:38:36,560 --> 00:38:37,920
Actually, I think so too.

1001
00:38:38,240 --> 00:38:39,280
It's not impossible

1002
00:38:39,520 --> 00:38:42,000
for us workers to have a good life.

1003
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:44,640
Mr. Dazhao, what do you mean?

1004
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:45,440
Will we be able to eat

1005
00:38:45,680 --> 00:38:47,360
dumplings whenever we want?

1006
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:48,400
Yes!

1007
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:53,680
Do you know there is a person called Marx?

1008
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:54,960
Don't know.

1009
00:38:56,160 --> 00:38:56,480
Who?

1010
00:38:57,600 --> 00:38:59,200
German. Big beard.

1011
00:38:59,680 --> 00:39:00,320
Ever heard of him?

1012
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,440
Don't you have a beard?

1013
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:03,440
His beard is a lot bigger than mine!

1014
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:06,560
Let me tell you something.

1015
00:39:07,200 --> 00:39:08,480
Marx has a view

1016
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:10,400
that the working class

1017
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:12,880
is the leader of human society.

1018
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:16,960
Only the society led by our working class

1019
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:19,920
is the most advanced society in the world.

1020
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:21,360
Is it?

1021
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:23,120
The most advanced society.

1022
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:25,120
This Marx said that the workers are leaders.

1023
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:26,080
Impossible.

1024
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,840
How can we workers be leaders?

1025
00:39:28,080 --> 00:39:28,960
What impossible?

1026
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,640
In Russia, there is a man called Lenin

1027
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:32,880
who based himself on this viewpoint and theory.

1028
00:39:33,200 --> 00:39:35,600
The people overthrew the bourgeois government.

1029
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:37,360
I know Russia is just north of us.

1030
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,440
The emperor of Russia is called the Tsar

1031
00:39:39,680 --> 00:39:40,800
and not Emperor.

1032
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:42,480
It's Tsar, without the "di".

1033
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:43,840
It sounds like "bean paste stuffing".

1034
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:44,880
Tsar!

1035
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:46,560
After the fall of the Tsar,

1036
00:39:46,640 --> 00:39:48,080
Lenin led the people

1037
00:39:48,160 --> 00:39:49,360
through armed uprising

1038
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,440
and overthrew the bourgeois provisional government,

1039
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:53,920
and then set up the first country

1040
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,640
led by the working class in human history,

1041
00:39:57,040 --> 00:39:58,560
which is called a socialist country

1042
00:39:59,040 --> 00:40:00,480
and also called the Soviet Union.

1043
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:03,120
A Soviet is a representative council.

1044
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:04,400
A Soviet authority

1045
00:40:04,720 --> 00:40:07,200
is an assembly of representatives of workers, peasants and soldiers.

1046
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:09,520
Right, what Shiyan said is correct.

1047
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:11,440
After the establishment of this government,

1048
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:13,360
the people did two things,

1049
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:14,880
two decrees were issued.

1050
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:16,480
The first

1051
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:18,160
-- I'll take this --

1052
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:22,560
is to announce that they will not participate in the World War.

1053
00:40:23,600 --> 00:40:24,560
They don't play with them anymore!

1054
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:25,920
How did you know that?

1055
00:40:26,160 --> 00:40:27,440
Just don't play with them!

1056
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:29,680
Don't play with these imperialists.

1057
00:40:30,080 --> 00:40:31,120
The second

1058
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,720
-- everyone will be interested in hearing this --

1059
00:40:35,360 --> 00:40:36,160
Say it!

1060
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:36,960
Say it!

1061
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:37,920
Sir, don't just talk!

1062
00:40:38,160 --> 00:40:38,800
Drink a bowl of water.

1063
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:40,640
I'll drink some water.

1064
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,680
Don't leave us in suspense.

1065
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:44,400
Right!

1066
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:46,640
This second thing is

1067
00:40:47,920 --> 00:40:49,440
the land is yours.

1068
00:40:49,680 --> 00:40:50,400
The land is yours.

1069
00:40:50,640 --> 00:40:51,440
The land is yours!

1070
00:40:51,840 --> 00:40:53,440
It's all ours!

1071
00:40:53,680 --> 00:40:56,720
Think about it. The land belongs to us.

1072
00:40:57,200 --> 00:40:59,920
Is it still difficult for us to have a good life?

1073
00:41:01,680 --> 00:41:03,280
We can be masters of our homes!

1074
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:04,000
Yeah!

1075
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:05,680
We can be masters of our own lives in the future.

1076
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:06,720
Mr. Dazhao,

1077
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:09,680
in this socialist country you just mentioned,

1078
00:41:10,267 --> 00:41:12,027
[Zhao Shiyan, styled Qinsheng, Student at The High School Affiliated to Beijing Normal University]

1079
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:12,320
does it mean that people no longer exploit people

1080
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:14,720
and no one bully us poor people?

1081
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:16,000
Exactly, that's what it means.

1082
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:17,840
Then do you have the bearded man you mentioned

1083
00:41:18,080 --> 00:41:19,360
and people like Lenin

1084
00:41:19,600 --> 00:41:20,640
in China?

1085
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:22,080
Yes, let's find him.

1086
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:23,440
Don't worry, everyone.

1087
00:41:23,600 --> 00:41:26,880
Now a group of people are looking for him.

1088
00:41:27,200 --> 00:41:28,480
You are the bearded man!

1089
00:41:31,360 --> 00:41:32,960
You are the bearded one!
